The paper discusses machine learning and information processing, which are core topics in computer science. The use of the Predictive Information Bottleneck Objective and the extension to include a validation data set suggest that the paper is likely to be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG), information theory (cs.IT), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
